01:06:20,760 --> 01:06:22,100
And I won't

1080
01:06:22,680 --> 01:06:24,850
leave you so soon.

1081
01:06:27,060 --> 01:06:28,480
I love you, my son.

1082
01:06:30,520 --> 01:06:34,070
I hope you live a long, happy life

1083
01:06:34,150 --> 01:06:36,740
with Mi-joo, Seo-jin, and Ye-jin.

1084
01:06:38,030 --> 01:06:40,410
And we'll meet again

1085
01:06:41,240 --> 01:06:43,580
on the day my prayer is answered.

1086
01:06:45,200 --> 01:06:46,950
From your bad mother.

1087
01:07:14,360 --> 01:07:15,610
Today

1088
01:07:17,070 --> 01:07:19,990
is the day propose to Mi-joo

1089
01:07:21,110 --> 01:07:23,450
to ask her to live
a long and happy life with me.

1090
01:07:25,280 --> 01:07:26,990
But you ruined everything.

1091
01:07:34,710 --> 01:07:36,710
Please watch over me

1092
01:07:37,840 --> 01:07:39,340
so that I won't be too nervous.

1093
01:07:41,130 --> 01:07:42,180
No.

1094
01:07:44,510 --> 01:07:45,890
Protect us.

1095
01:07:54,940 --> 01:07:55,980
Lee Mi-joo!

1096
01:07:56,860 --> 01:08:00,690
You're under arrest for becoming my wife!

1097
01:08:00,780 --> 01:08:04,120
You don't have the right to remain silent.

1098
01:08:04,200 --> 01:08:06,410
You cannot ask your mother for help
when we argue.

1099
01:08:06,490 --> 01:08:07,790
How childish.

1100
01:08:07,870 --> 01:08:09,830
This isn't a proposal.

1101
01:08:10,410 --> 01:08:12,160
-Why not?
-What you just said

1102
01:08:12,920 --> 01:08:14,880
might be used against you later in life.

1103
01:08:14,960 --> 01:08:16,250
So watch out, okay?

1104
01:08:18,420 --> 01:08:19,920
-This won't do.
-What?

1105
01:08:20,010 --> 01:08:21,670
All right. I need your help.

1106
01:08:22,220 --> 01:08:23,220
-What?
-All right.

1107
01:08:27,850 --> 01:08:28,720
Lee Mi-joo!

1108
01:08:28,810 --> 01:08:30,770
I saved your life three times.

1109
01:08:30,850 --> 01:08:32,690
So even if I get so annoying,

1110
01:08:32,770 --> 01:08:34,190
even if we argue,

1111
01:08:34,270 --> 01:08:36,610
and even if I get downright childish,

1112
01:08:38,190 --> 01:08:41,820
promise to live with me happily
for the rest of our lives.

1113
01:08:48,120 --> 01:08:49,450
All right, go ahead.

1114
01:08:49,540 --> 01:08:50,830
-Come here.
-Go to mommy.

1115
01:08:50,910 --> 01:08:53,660
-No!
-Oh, no!

1116
01:09:32,870 --> 01:09:35,660
-Kang-ho! Hang on, I…
-We have to look good.

1117
01:09:36,290 --> 01:09:39,670
Come on, think of our age.

1118
01:09:39,750 --> 01:09:43,010
-He is a napa cabbage flower
-Napa cabbage flower

1119
01:09:43,090 --> 01:09:47,760
A new wind will blow

1120
01:09:47,840 --> 01:09:48,800
SAM-SIK'S MILL

1121
01:09:48,890 --> 01:09:51,720
I don't even eat marinated crabs

1122
01:09:51,810 --> 01:09:53,350
because it's so good
I'd steal to eat them!

1123
01:09:53,430 --> 01:09:54,560
I hate stray cats even more.

1124
01:09:54,640 --> 01:09:56,640
They're like little thieves.

1125
01:09:56,730 --> 01:09:59,190
Do you know how shocked I was

1126
01:09:59,270 --> 01:10:01,520
when The Thieves was released?

1127
01:10:01,610 --> 01:10:03,320
Hey!

1128
